FBIS4-9574 "dreeu082_c_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-082 Daily Report 27 Apr 1994 CZECH REPUBLIC Minister of Education Petr Pitha Resigns Minister of Education Petr Pitha Resigns LD2704113394 Prague Radiozurnal Radio Network in Czech 1100 GMT 27 Apr 94 LD2704113394 Prague Radiozurnal Radio Network Czech BFN [Text] Having considered the state of his health, the Czech minister of education, Petr Pitha, has told Prime Minister Vaclav Klaus today that he is resigning. Petr Pitha has been unable to work for several weeks. Asked who should replace him in his post, Pitha said he did not know.
